<i>adverb</i>: 진배없이 [진배업씨], 똑같이 [똑까치], 다름없이 [다르멉씨], 균등히 [균등히], 골고루 [골고루], 고루고루 [고루고루], 고루 [고루] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>진배없이 [진배업씨]</dt><br>
<dd>equally; similarly</dd><br>
<dd>그보다 못하거나 다른 점이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being no worse than, as good as, or no different from something.</dd><br>
<dt>똑같이 [똑까치]</dt><br>
<dd>1. equally; evenly</dd><br>
<dd>사물의 모양, 분량, 성질 등이 서로 조금도 다른 데가 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that two or more things are not a bit different from each other in shape, amount, quality, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. identically</dd><br>
<dd>사람의 외모, 태도, 행동 등이 닮아 아주 비슷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which two or more people are very similar to each other in appearance, attitude, behavior, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. same</dd><br>
<dd>새롭거나 특별한 것이 전혀 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without anything new or special.</dd><br>
<dd>4. simultaneously</dd><br>
<dd>동시에. 또는 거의 같은 시간에.</dd><br>
<dd>At the same time, or at the almost same time.</dd><br>
<dt>다름없이 [다르멉씨]</dt><br>
<dd>similarly; equally</dd><br>
<dd>서로 같거나 비슷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the same or similar manner.</dd><br>
<dt>균등히 [균등히]</dt><br>
<dd>evenly; equally</dd><br>
<dd>차이가 없이 고르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In equal amounts without difference.</dd><br>
<dt>골고루 [골고루]</dt><br>
<dd>1. equally; evenly</dd><br>
<dd>많고 적음의 차이가 없이 비슷비슷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In equal amounts without any difference in quantity.</dd><br>
<dd>2. all; everything</dd><br>
<dd>뻬놓지 않고 이것저것 모두.</dd><br>
<dd>Everything without leaving anything out.</dd><br>
<dt>고루고루 [고루고루]</dt><br>
<dd>1. evenly; equally</dd><br>
<dd>많고 적음의 차이가 없이 비슷비슷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In equal amounts without difference in quantity.</dd><br>
<dd>2. all; everything</dd><br>
<dd>빼놓지 않고 이것저것 모두.</dd><br>
<dd>Everything without leaving anything out.</dd><br>
<dt>고루 [고루]</dt><br>
<dd>1. evenly; equally</dd><br>
<dd>많고 적음의 차이가 없이 비슷하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In equal amounts without difference in quantity.</dd><br>
<dd>2. all of</dd><br>
<dd>빼놓지 않고 이것저것 모두.</dd><br>
<dd>Everything without leaving anything out.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>